node.text: Lunella Lafayette and her twenty-foot dinosaur are BACK in Marvel Comics’ 'Moon Girl and Devil Dinosaur'. In 2022, the biggest brain in the world and her dino companion bring new meaning to the term “Marvel Team-Up” in a tale that promises to…Shake Your World. #MarvelComics

node.text: Dan Slott is joined by Carlos Pacheco and Rachael Stott for Marvel Comics’ 'Fantastic Four: Reckoning War', an epic saga over 15 years in the making. The original secret war of the Marvel Universe has been reignited and we are finally at…Our Day Of Reckoning. #MarvelComics

node.text: Marvel Comics’ 'She-Hulk', from Rainbow Rowell and Rogê Antônio, finds lawyer Jennifer Walters trying to put her rage-filled days behind her. But when a friend from her past comes knocking with a mystery she can’t resist, She-Hulk gets…Back To Bashing. #MarvelComics

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Marvel Entertainment on August 31, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: In the tradition of 'House of X' and 'Powers of X', Benjamin Percy, Joshua Cassara, and Federico Vicentini present Marvel Comics’ 'X Lives of Wolverine' and 'X Deaths of Wolverine' - Two interlocked tales about what happens to Wolverine when…His Pasts Meet His Future. #MarvelComics

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Marvel Entertainment on August 31, 2021. May be an image of text that says '#MARVELCOMICS MARVEL TIMELESS JED MAcKAY JOE BENNETT KEV WALKER MARK BAGLEY DECEMBER 2021 2021 MARVEL'.

node.text: The future of the Marvel Universe is here, and 'Timeless' is where it all begins. Jed MacKay, Kev Walker, Joe Bennett, Mark Bagley, and more help Kang set the stage for the Marvel Universe in 2022, in a story that will show…the Future is Timeless. #MarvelComics

node.text: In Marvel Comics’ 'Avengers Forever', Jason Aaron and Aaron Kuder present an all-new series that will redefine the Avengers as…the Multiverse’s Mightiest Heroes. #MarvelComics
